'''Beatrice Bocci''' (born 8 April 1970) is an [[Italian people|Italian]] [[showgirl]], beauty pageant winner and [[television presenter]].<ref name="Beatrice">{{cite web|url=http://www.liquida.it/beatrice-bocci/|title= Beatrice bocci: "io vittima del sistema della tv"-foto|publisher=Liquida|date= |accessdate=25 April 2014}}</ref> In 1994 she was crowned Miss Tuscany and later placed first runner-up at [[Miss Italia]] 1994.<ref name="Beatrice1">{{cite web|url=http://archiviostorico.corriere.it/1994/settembre/04/piu_bella_Alessandra_co_0_94090411453.shtml |title=Esplora il significato del termine |publisher=Corriere Della Sera |date= |accessdate=25 April 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426232314/http://archiviostorico.corriere.it/1994/settembre/04/piu_bella_Alessandra_co_0_94090411453.shtml |archivedate=April 26, 2014 }}</ref> She has hosted the shows  Su le mani and Va ora in onda both on [[RAI 1]].<ref name="Beatrice"/>

